renders without error | Exit code 0 |\n  Line 358: | AC030-013 | Helm lint passes | Exit code 0 |\n  Line 364: | Helm | 3.x | Chart rendering and installation |\n  Line 378: - Helm hook-based upgrade migrations\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 1: # Delta Spec: AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n  Line 5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the Helm Chart templates and values configuration for deploying AgentCube to Kubernetes, providing a reusable, configurable deployment mechanism for the Workload Manager, Router, optional Volcano scheduler, and associated RBAC resources.\n  Line 9: - **AR**: AR-030\n  Line 10: - **Module**: `manifests`\n  Line 19: AgentCube requires a standardized deployment mechanism to Kubernetes clusters. The deployment/spec.md document defines the expected chart structure, but the actual template files need implementation. The Helm chart enables reproducible deployments, configuration management via values.yaml, namespace-scoped installations, optional components (RBAC, Volcano scheduler), and CRD lifecycle management.\n  Line 25: ### AR-030-001: Chart 结构与元数据\n  Line 27: The Helm chart SHALL provide proper structure and metadata for Helm 3 compatibility.\n  Line 29: #### Scenario: AR-030-001-A — Chart.yaml 包含正确的元数据\n  Line 31: - **GIVEN** a chart directory at `manifests/charts/base/`\n  Line 32: - **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is executed\n  Line 36: #### Scenario: AR-030-001-B — values.yaml 包含所有必需配置项\n  Line 42: #### Scenario: AR-030-001-C — 目录结构完整\n  Line 50: ### AR-030-002: Helm 安装与 Namespace 管理\n  Line 52: The system SHALL support installing/upgrading the AgentCube stack with Helm from `manifests/charts/base`, including namespace creation.\n  Line 54: #### Scenario: AR-030-002-A — Helm install 创建 namespace\n  Line 56: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster and Helm 3 available\n  Line 58: - **WHEN** `helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube --create-namespace` is executed\n  Line 62: #### Scenario: AR-030-002-B — Helm upgrade 成功渲染模板\n  Line 66: - **WHEN** `helm upgrade agentcube manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube` runs\n  Line 71: ### AR-030-003: Redis 环境变量注入\n  Line 75: #### Scenario: AR-030-003-A — Workload Manager 接收 Redis 配置\n  Line 82: #### Scenario: AR-030-003-B — Router 接收 Redis 配置\n  Line 89: #### Scenario: AR-030-003-C — Redis 密码可为空\n  Line 97: ### AR-030-004: Workload Manager Deployment 配置\n  Line 101: #### Scenario: AR-030-004-A — 默认副本数\n  Line 107: #### Scenario: AR-030-004-B — 自定义副本数\n  Line 113: #### Scenario: AR-030-004-C — 容器镜像可配置\n  Line 119: #### Scenario: AR-030-004-D — Service 端口配置\n  Line 126: #### Scenario: AR-030-004-E — 健康检查探针\n  Line 133: #### Scenario: AR-030-004-F — 资源限制可配置\n  Line 139: #### Scenario: AR-030-004-G — 额外环境变量\n  Line 147: ### AR-030-005: Router Deployment 配置\n  Line 151: #### Scenario: AR-030-005-A — Router 默认副本数\n  Line 157: #### Scenario: AR-030-005-B — Router 连接到 Workload Manager\n  Line 163: #### Scenario: AR-030-005-C — Router 镜像可配置\n  Line 169: #### Scenario: AR-030-005-D — Router Service 类型可配置\n  Line 175: #### Scenario: AR-030-005-E — Router 健康检查\n  Line 182: #### Scenario: AR-030-005-F — Router 资源限制\n  Line 188: #### Scenario: AR-030-005-G — Router 调试模式\n  Line 196: ### AR-030-006: Workload Manager RBAC\n  Line 200: #### Scenario: AR-030-006-A — ServiceAccount 创建\n  Line 206: #### Scenario: AR-030-006-B — ClusterRole 权限\n  Line 219: #### Scenario: AR-030-006-C — ClusterRoleBinding 绑定\n  Line 227: ### AR-030-007: Router 命名空间 RBAC (可选)\n  Line 231: #### Scenario: AR-030-007-A — RBAC 默认禁用\n  Line 235: - **THEN** Router optional RBAC manifests SHALL NOT be emitted\n  Line 237: #### Scenario: AR-030-007-B — RBAC 启用时创建\n  Line 246: #### Scenario: AR-030-007-C — Router 使用专用 ServiceAccount\n  Line 254: ### AR-030-008: Volcano Agent Scheduler (可选)\n  Line 258: #### Scenario: AR-030-008-A — 默认不启用\n  Line 264: #### Scenario: AR-030-008-B — 启用时创建资源\n  Line 276: #### Scenario: AR-030-008-C — Volcano 镜像可配置\n  Line 284: ### AR-030-009: CRD 清单\n  Line 286: The system SHALL ship `CustomResourceDefinition` manifests for `agentruntimes` and `codeinterpreters` in the chart's `crds/` directory.\n  Line 288: #### Scenario: AR-030-009-A — CRD 目录存在\n  Line 294: #### Scenario: AR-030-009-B — AgentRuntime CRD\n  Line 296: - **GIVEN** the CRD manifests are present\n  Line 302: #### Scenario: AR-030-009-C — CodeInterpreter CRD\n  Line 304: - **GIVEN** the CRD manifests are present\n  Line 312: ### AR-030-010: Helm 模板验证\n  Line 314: The chart SHALL pass Helm validation and render correctly.\n  Line 316: #### Scenario: AR-030-010-A — Helm lint 通过\n  Line 318: - **GIVEN** the chart at `manifests/charts/base/`\n  Line 319: - **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is executed\n  Line 322: #### Scenario: AR-030-010-B — 模板渲染无错误\n  Line 325: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` runs\n  Line 329: #### Scenario: AR-030-010-C — 完整渲染包含所有资源\n  Line 354: - Helm hook-based upgrade migrations\n  Line 364: | deployment/design.md | Helm chart specification |\n  Line 366: | Helm 3 | Chart rendering and installation |\n  Line 377: | AC030-003 | Helm install creates namespace | `kubectl get ns` |\n  Line 387: | AC030-013 | Helm template renders without error | `helm template` exit code |\n  Line 388: | AC030-014 | Helm lint passes | `helm lint` exit code |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n  Line 5: Implement the Helm Chart templates and values configuration for deploying AgentCube to Kubernetes, providing a reusable, configurable deployment mechanism for the Workload Manager, Router, optional Volcano scheduler, and associated RBAC resources.\n  Line 11: AgentCube requires a standardized deployment mechanism to Kubernetes clusters. Currently, the system lacks a formal Helm chart for production deployments. The deployment/design.md and deployment/spec.md documents define the expected chart structure, but the actual template files need implementation.\n  Line 13: The Helm chart enables:\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 159 matches (59 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":159,"truncated":true},"title":"AR-030|manifests|Helm","time":{"start":1775871581086,"end":1775871581102}}}}
